auth.query: select o from User o where o.login = :login

roles.query: select o.id from Role o where o.user.login = :login

query.sqlContent:
select v.bancId, v.created, v.dbid, v.dbname, v.eventoExecucaoId, v.logMode, v.nome, v.openMode, v.platformName, v.protectionLevel, v.protectionMode 
from VmOrclDatabase v where v.bancId = :bancId 
and v.eventoExecucaoId = (select max(x.eventoExecucaoId) from  VmOrclDatabase x where v.bancId = x.bancId and x.dataInicio >= :dataInicio)

select v.bancId, v.eventoExecucaoId, v.nome, v.hostName, v.status, v.parallel, v.archiver, v.databaseStatus, v.startupTime, v.instanceName from VmOrclInstance v
where v.bancId = :bancId 
and v.eventoExecucaoId = (select max(x.eventoExecucaoId) from  VmOrclInstance x where v.bancId = x.bancId and x.dataInicio >= :dataInicio)

select v from VmOrclVersion v
where v.bancId = :bancId 
and v.eventoExecucaoId = (select max(x.eventoExecucaoId) from  VmOrclVersion x where v.bancId = x.bancId)

select substring(v.line,0,90) as line from VmOrclSistemaOperacional v
where v.bancId = :bancId 
and v.eventoExecucaoId = (select max(x.eventoExecucaoId) from  VmOrclSistemaOperacional x where v.bancId = x.bancId and x.dataInicio between :dataInicio and :dataFim )
and v.line is not null
and length(v.line) > 2
order by v.seqResultado
select v.clientes.nome, v.nome from VwBancos v where v.id = :bancId

select v from VmOrclResourceLimit v
where v.bancId = :bancId 
and v.eventoExecucaoId = (select max(x.eventoExecucaoId) from  VmOrclResourceLimit x where v.bancId = x.bancId and x.dataInicio between :dataInicio and :dataFim )
order by v.seqResultado

select MIN(b.qtdeSessoesAtivas) as minAtivas, MAX(b.qtdeSessoesAtivas) as maxAtivas, AVG(b.qtdeSessoesAtivas) as avgAtivas, a.numMaxSessoes as numMaxSessoes 
from BancosStatusSessoes b, VwBancos a 
where a.id = b.bancId and b.bancId = :bancId AND b.dataGeracao BETWEEN :dataInicio AND :dataFim group by numMaxSessoes

select MIN(b.qtdeSessoesAtivas) as minAtivas, MAX(b.qtdeSessoesAtivas) as maxAtivas, AVG(b.qtdeSessoesAtivas) as avgAtivas, SQL('FCN_DATE_HOUR(?)', b.dataGeracao) AS dataHora,  
 a.numMaxSessoes as numMaxSessoes from BancosStatusSessoes b, VwBancos a 
where a.id = b.bancId and b.bancId = :bancId AND b.dataGeracao BETWEEN :dataInicio AND :dataFim group by dataHora, numMaxSessoes order by dataHora

select MIN(b.currentUtilization) as minAtivas, MAX(b.currentUtilization) as maxAtivas, AVG(b.currentUtilization) as avgAtivas, SQL('FCN_DATE_DAY_HOUR(?)', b.dataInicio) AS dataHora, 
SQL('TRUNC(?)', b.dataInicio) AS data 
from VwOrclSessionsCurrent b 
where  b.bancId = :bancId AND b.dataInicio BETWEEN :dataInicio AND :dataFim group by data, dataHora order by data, dataHora

select MIN(b.currentUtilization) as minAtivas, MAX(b.currentUtilization) as maxAtivas, AVG(b.currentUtilization) as avgAtivas 
from VwOrclSessionsCurrent b 
where  b.bancId = :bancId AND b.dataInicio BETWEEN :dataInicio AND :dataFim

select MIN(b.currentUtilization) as minAtivas, MAX(b.currentUtilization) as maxAtivas, AVG(b.currentUtilization) as avgAtivas,  SQL('FCN_DATE_HOUR(?)', b.dataInicio) AS dataHora 
from VwOrclSessionsCurrent b 
where  b.bancId = :bancId AND b.dataInicio BETWEEN :dataInicio AND :dataFim group by dataHora order by dataHora

select sum(v.qtdLocks) as qtdLocks , SQL('FCN_DATE_DAY_HOUR(?)', d.dataInicio) AS dataHora, SQL('TRUNC(?)', d.dataInicio) AS data 
from VmOrclLocksEventos v, DataGraficoAux d where v.bancId = :bancId 
AND d.dataInicio BETWEEN :dataInicio AND :dataFim 
AND v.dataInicio BETWEEN d.dataInicio AND d.dataFim
group by dataHora, data  
order by dataHora, data

select v from VyOrclTablespaces v where v.bancId = :bancId AND v.dataInicio BETWEEN :dataInicio AND :dataFim 
AND v.eventoExecucaoId = ( SELECT MAX(x.eventoExecucaoId) FROM VyOrclTablespaces x WHERE v.bancId = x.bancId AND x.dataInicio BETWEEN :dataInicio AND :dataFim ) 
order by v.tablespaceName asc

select v from VwOrclAsm v
where v.bancId = :bancId 
and v.eventoExecucaoId = (select max(x.eventoExecucaoId) from  VwOrclAsm x where v.bancId = x.bancId and x.dataInicio between :dataInicio and :dataFim )
order by v.seqResultado

select v from VmOrclMemory v
where v.bancId = :bancId 
and v.eventoExecucaoId = (select max(x.eventoExecucaoId) from  VmOrclMemory x where v.bancId = x.bancId and x.dataInicio between :dataInicio and :dataFim )
order by v.name

select MIN(b.hitRatio) as minHitRatio, MAX(b.hitRatio) as maxHitRatio, SQL('FCN_DATE_DAY_HOUR(?)', b.dataInicio) AS dataHora
from VmOrclBufferRatio b
where b.bancId = :bancId AND b.dataInicio BETWEEN :dataInicio AND :dataFim group by dataHora order by dataHora

select v from VmOrclParameters v
where v.bancId = :bancId 
and v.eventoExecucaoId = (select max(x.eventoExecucaoId) from  VmOrclParameters x where v.bancId = x.bancId and x.dataInicio between :dataInicio and :dataFim )
order by v.nomeParametro

select SUM(v.archiveHoraMbytes), SQL('FCN_DATE_MONTH(?)', v.dataInicio) as dataMes, v.dataInicio 
from VxOrclArchivedHour v where v.bancId = :bancId AND v.dataInicio BETWEEN :dataInicio AND :dataFim 
group by dataMes, v.dataInicio  order by v.dataInicio asc
select AVG(v.qtdFiles) + SQL('STDDEV(?)',v.qtdFiles) as alertaLimite from VxOrclArchived v  where v.bancId = :bancId AND v.dataInicio BETWEEN :dataInicio AND :dataFim
select v from VwPolomsgAvisos v order by v.dataAviso desc
